profile: A&E Tile Design offers professional tile design and installation for all your tiling needs. Whether you are in need of some design/product suggestions or are simply in need of a quality tile installation, A&E Tile Design has got you covered. With over 15 years experience in the tiling industry, we have extensive knowledge on all products associated with tile installation. While we specialize in custom homes, we also do anything from small renovations to large commercial projects. We pride ourselves in our work and approach each new project, big or small, with confidence and enthusiasm. Call A&E Tile Design today at (705)888-3731 and let us help make your dreams a reality.
